{
  "stem": "3855.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Charles Karl Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "H-I-R-S-C-H.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no other names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 19th, 1914.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll be 81 in September.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Vienna, which is now Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time of my birth, it was the Austro-Hungarian Kingdom-- monarchy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "V-- as in victory-- I-E-N-NA.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-U-S-T-R-I-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so not to go to extremes, I'm almost tempted to say marvelous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very cosmopolitan, intellectual city-- the wellspring of many movements in the arts, in medicine, and not to speak of, psychology.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, who admired the old monarchy, ascribed to the fact that Austria lived in peace since 1848 under the emperor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that long period of peace permitted the growth and flourishing of the various arts, sciences, and commerce, as well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In addition to the fact that the Jews during the '48 revolution were released from the ghetto, permitted them within a few years to gain tremendous prominence in the arts, in the literature, in the sciences, medicine, and particularly in commerce, in the old Austrian monarchy.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My recollections of Vienna before the war are most pleasant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really, as a youngster, did not encounter anti-Semitism, I must say, despite the fact that I moved in mixed groups in my school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of my best friends was a very devout Catholic, whom I will later mention.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, nothing is permanent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing is fixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing is stable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everything is in flux.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it certainly changed rapidly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember it very distinctly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in the 2nd district, which, before '48, was the Jewish ghetto, and maintained a very intensive Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The saving grace was that we lived right at the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the 1st district, which was the finest, so it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, I lived in Hollandstrasse, Holland Street number 2.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
